---
const benefits = [
  'In good months, Storehouse helps you store the surplus automatically',
  'In lean months, you draw from your reserves without guilt',
];
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">
        Finally, a budget that gets irregular income.
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-600">
        If your income changes month to month — commission, freelance, business ownership — traditional budgets break immediately.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-storehouse-700 mb-6">
          The Joseph Principle
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          {benefits.map((benefit) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-left">
              <svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 text-storehouse-500 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
              <span class="text-lg text-slate-700">{benefit}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-storehouse-600 italic">
        Store today. Thrive tomorrow.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
